    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it's not ideal but i'm just so tired and i feel like i'm talking about way too much. i only had one glass and i'm not even drunk, just relaxed. if i take it now, isn't it just gonna help me sleep deeper? like, would it actually be life threatening or am i just overthinking it? i really need to sleep tonight.",
