      "content": "i hear you but it seems a bit extreme for just one glass of wine. i've heard people say that a little bit of alcohol actually helps sedative meds work more effectively. if i just take a half dose of the zolpidem or something, wouldn't that make it safer? i just really need to know if it's truly a \"life or death\" thing right now because i'm desperate for sleep.",
